! Title: Hide YouTube 'Mix' Playlist
! Description: Hide 'Mix' playlist on YouTube.
! Homepage: https://github.com/h1toru/filterlist
!
! Last modified: 2025-01-07 12:57:24 UTC
! Format: Adblock
! Entries: 2
!
! Report any problem at https://github.com/h1toru/filterlist/issues
!————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————!

! Hide Mix playlist
! [info]: match playlist that has '&start_radio=1' in the URL and has 'Mix' badge on the thumbnail.
! [note]: using `h3[title^="Mix - "]` method will match playlist name that begins with 'Mix - ' even if it's not actually a mix playlist generated by YouTube.
www.youtube.com##:is(ytd-rich-item-renderer.ytd-rich-grid-renderer, yt-lockup-view-model.ytd-item-section-renderer):has(a[href$="&start_radio=1"], yt-thumbnail-overlay-badge-view-model .badge-shape-wiz__text:has-text(/^Mix$/))
! Hide 'Mixes' filter chip
www.youtube.com##yt-chip-cloud-chip-renderer:has([title="Mixes"])